title: Grateful Dead Live at Rosemont Horizon on 1988-04-14
description:
Set 1

Jack Straw, West L.A. Fadeaway, Mama Tried-> Big River, Althea, When I Paint My Masterpiece, Bird Song, Promised Land

Set 2

Box Of Rain, Iko Iko, Estimated Prophet-> Eyes Of The World-> Drums-> Jam-> The Wheel-> Black Peter-> Throwing Stones-> Not Fade Away, E: Black Muddy River

reviews.review_text: Oh God Right out of the gate, this is the kind of show I would have exploded through the roof from Garcia's first solo in Jack Straw and not come down for the next 24 hours. 20 years later I can still feel what this show would have felt like for me. I was one of those rare deadheads who went to shows to listen to the music, and they were ON this night.
